 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lady-gaga-dramatic-new-single-disease-3806194">“疾病”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-gothic-music-video-for-lady-gagas-surprise-new-single-abracadabra-3833942">“ Abracadabra”的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-reveals-die-with-a-smile-with-bruno-mars-huge-part-new-album-3824137">“笑容”</a> 。昨天，她透露了这张专辑的完整歌曲集，其中包括DJ和制片人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gesaffelstein">Gesaffelstein</a>的功能 -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-lady-gagas-mayhem-tracklist-3839142">在此处查看专辑的完整曲目列表</a>。</p><p> Gaga最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-talks-true-chaos-of-new-album-3820703">开放了粉丝可以从“混乱”中期望的“真正的混乱”</a> 。她说，专辑“只是想尽可能多地推动声音”。她解释说，她希望LP在发生更积极的事情之前捕捉挣扎的“看光”的感觉。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830907" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830907" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830907" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/lady-gaga@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830907" class="wp-caption-text">嘎嘎小姐。学分：杰夫·克拉维兹（Jeff Kravitz）/电影杂志</figcaption></figure><p>她补充说：“还有其他时刻与爱有关，这是超级梦幻的。” “对我来说，那是真正的混乱。有时候很难看到光线，但是我认为有时会使内在混乱变得更加困难的是，有时您会瞥见阳光，因为您就像，“男人，我希望太阳能一直闪耀，然后它使您想起您所缺少的东西。”</p><p>这位歌手还将新唱片描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-teases-chaotic-and-genre-bending-new-album-its-very-fun-3815070">“混乱”，“流派弯曲”和“非常有趣”</a> 。她说：“当我写作，制作和唱歌时，我总是在借鉴我对音乐史以及在我面前的许多艺术家和制作人的了解。” “这样，这张专辑是对我成为我自己的许多音乐的庆祝活动，因为当我回到深色的流行流行风格时，我对音乐的所有早期体验都出现了。”</p><p>在其他地方，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2025-lady-gaga-green-day-post-malone-travis-scott-lead-line-up-3814558">还将与Post Malone和Green Day一起在4月份的Coachella 2025头条新闻</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-to-celebrate-mayhem-release-by-pulling-double-duty-on-snl-3839233">Lady Gaga的邮报庆祝“混乱”发行，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
